(Finding #1: [High] Unsafe Option datum deconstruction in collateral.spend) Tj T*
(  Detector: unsafe-datum-deconstruction) Tj T*
(  Module: collateral) Tj T*
(  Location: validators/collateral.ak:24) Tj T*
(Description: Datum parameter 'datum' is Option<T> but handler never uses `expect) Tj T*
(    Some\(..\) = datum`. Accessing the datum without safe deconstruction may cause runtime) Tj T*
(    errors.) Tj T*
(Recommendation: Use `expect Some\(datum\) = datum_opt` to safely deconstruct the Optional) Tj T*
(    datum.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
