(Finding #8: [Info] Handler collateral.spend produces outputs without minimum ADA check) Tj T*
(  Detector: missing-min-ada-check) Tj T*
(  Module: collateral) Tj T*
(  Location: validators/collateral.ak:24) Tj T*
(Description: Handler creates outputs but doesn't verify the minimum ADA \(lovelace\)) Tj T*
(    requirement. Cardano requires every UTXO to contain a minimum amount of ADA. Note: The) Tj T*
(    Cardano ledger enforces this as a protocol rule — transactions with outputs below) Tj T*
(    the minimum are rejected at submission time, so this is not exploitable but may cause) Tj T*
(    unexpected transaction failures.) Tj T*
(Recommendation: Ensure outputs include sufficient ADA using) Tj T*
(    `value.from_lovelace\(2_000_000\)` or check with `value.lovelace_of\(output.value\) >=) Tj T*
(    min_required`.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
